Regular tidying keeps a Srinagar home livable, but a **professional deep clean** tackles the grime that daily routines miss — grease behind stoves, limescale in bathrooms, dust in ceiling corners, and buildup in hard-to-reach spaces. Whether you are preparing for guests, moving in, or recovering after renovation, deep cleaning restores a fresh, healthy living environment.

## What is included in home deep cleaning?

Depending on your booking, a deep clean in Srinagar may cover:

- **Kitchen** — countertops, cabinets (exterior), sink, backsplash, appliance exteriors, floor scrubbing
- **Bathrooms** — tiles, toilet, shower, mirrors, fixtures, exhaust fan grilles
- **Bedrooms and living areas** — dusting, vacuuming, floor mopping, window sills
- **Common areas** — hallways, stairs, entrance, balcony sweeping
- **Add-ons** — sofa shampooing, carpet cleaning, inside-cabinet cleaning (request when booking)

Deep cleaning goes beyond a quick sweep. Providers bring supplies and focus on areas that accumulate dirt over weeks or months.

## When should you book deep cleaning in Srinagar?

- **After renovation or construction** — dust on every surface
- **Before festivals or family gatherings** — Eid, weddings, house parties
- **Seasonal refresh** — post-winter or pre-monsoon cleaning
- **Move-in or move-out** — empty or furnished flats in Rajbagh, Nowgam, Lal Chowk, and beyond
- **When regular help is not enough** — busy households that need a thorough reset

## How to prepare your home

- Declutter surfaces so cleaners can access counters, floors, and shelves
- Secure valuables and mention fragile items
- Ensure water and electricity are available
- Share the number of rooms, bathrooms, and any special requests (pet hair, allergy-safe products)

Most providers bring their own cleaning products. Mention if you need eco-friendly or fragrance-free supplies.

## Home cleaning vs office cleaning

Panun Kaergar also offers **office and commercial cleaning** for shops, clinics, and workplaces. Home deep cleaning is tailored to residential layouts — kitchens, bedrooms, and family living spaces — with flexible timing around your schedule.

## How often should you deep clean?

Most Srinagar households benefit from a full deep clean every three to six months, or after major events and renovations. Families with young children, pets, or allergy concerns may prefer quarterly visits. Regular light cleaning between deep cleans keeps maintenance manageable.

